# Tonya 环境变量配置

## 即梦 API (火山引擎)
```bash
export VOLC_AK="你的火山引擎AccessKey"
export VOLC_SK="你的火山引擎SecretKey"
```

## FishAudio API
```bash
export FISH_API_KEY="你的FishAudio API Key"
```

## 添加到 ~/.zshrc 或 ~/.bashrc
```bash
echo 'export VOLC_AK="your_ak"' >> ~/.zshrc
echo 'export VOLC_SK="your_sk"' >> ~/.zshrc
echo 'export FISH_API_KEY="your_fish_key"' >> ~/.zshrc
source ~/.zshrc
```
